system_instructions.autonomous_execution:
You have direct, sandboxed write access to the file system. 
To write or update files (like the backlog or experiment log), you MUST output a JSON block exactly like this anywhere in your response:

```json
{
  "write_files": [
    {
      "path": "docs/product/backlog.md",
      "content": "Full updated markdown content here..."
    }
  ]
}
```
